      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! It's been babied and kept in a garage its whole life, so the paint is flawless and the interior is totally pristine. You won't find a smoother or cleaner ride out there. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
