    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is mechanically pristine, with preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service already completed. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast shifts, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures precise torque vectoring. The chassis is factory-firm with zero bushing play, and the EDC (Electronic Damper Control) system functions flawlessly across all damping maps. The exterior retains its factory paint depth with no swirl marks, and the underbody is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation, reflecting its protected, climate-controlled history.",
      "price": 47800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
