    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, presenting in a condition that challenges even brand-new showroom models. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or any imperfections, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is flawless; the premium leather remains supple with no compression on the bolsters, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a fastidious service history that documents preventative maintenance far beyond the factory requirements. For the buyer who demands a pristine, investment-grade example without compromise, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
